{"tid":2207407,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"四眼：熱血鳳凰計劃啫係國泰民安人道支援","createTime":"2020-09-18T06:55:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T07:15:27.000Z","uid":5843,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f00ae854d20157d7b41ff3ded5dae39a80b2a687","tid":2207407,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T06:55:20.000Z","msg":"有 #黃色區議員 問及「#熱血鳳凰計劃」搞成點，「國泰民安 人道支援」嘅前身就係「熱血鳳凰計劃」。<br />\n<br />\n前者主力協助不幸惹上官非嘅抗爭者，老實講當年社會大眾普遍根本就唔關心佢哋死活，甚至認為部份「無名無姓」抗爭者係鬼，或者罪有應得，泛民大台亦講明唔會提供協助。<br />\n<br />\n去年「熱血鳳凰計劃」為咗幫助更多有需要人士，特別照顧大台、黃色區議員消極跟進，甚至拒絕提供協助嘅個案，因而成立「國民支援」。<br />\n<br />\n現在我哋每月最少直接援助30個以上個案，開支超過10萬港元。能夠提供任何形式協助者，歡迎直接與我聯絡。<br />\n<br />\np.s. 逸澤王頴思 議員，以前就係「熱血鳳凰計劃」秘書。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://civicpassion.hk/index.php/portfolio-item/project-phoenix/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcivicpassion.hk%2Findex.php%2Fportfolio-item%2Fproject-phoenix%2F&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdQEiaVT8aWta%2BTWQuzHxyy8%3D&h=2fe61bc1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://civicpassion.hk/index.php/portfolio-item/project-phoenix/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gK4jN7X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgK4jN7X.png&h=72c3069b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"706f11077d361f56bee982fd8339b075c82814fb","tid":2207407,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T06:55:52.000Z","msg":"王姑娘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b66234ff8ca9554b4b4ce8bed1d48b7d6d53ba1f","tid":2207407,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T07:10:43.000Z","msg":"射撚滿 真系on9仔<br />\n<br />\n區議員 系制度一員（在明）<br />\n一言一行當可理直氣壯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你班熱狗 搞社運抗爭（在暗）<br />\n有咩行差踏錯隨時身陷囹圄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\